MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 650

RESERVING CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED AT BARANGAY BANTULINAO, CALAUAG, QUEZON, ISLAND OF LUZON, FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF THE BANTULINAO ELEMENTARY AND HIGH SCHOOLS

Upon the recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and pursuant to the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale, entry, disposition or settlement and reserve for school site purposes of the BARTULINAO ELEMENTARY AND HIGH SHOOLS under the administration of the Department of Education, subject to private rights, if any there be, certain parcels of land of the public domain situated at Barangay Bantulinao, Calauag, Quezon, Island of Luzon, which parcel of land are more particularly described as follows:

LOT NO. 6180-A, CSD-04-019187-D BARANGAY BANTULINAO HIGH SCHOOL

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot No. 6180-A, Csd-04-019187-D, being a portion of Lot 6180, Pls-45, Calauag Public Land Subdivision), situated in Brgy. Bantulinao, Municipality of Calauag, Province of Quezon, Island of Luzon. Bounded on the SE. and S., along lines 1-2-3 by Lot 6180-B, Csd-04-019187-D; on the W., along line 3-4 by lot 6167, Pls-45 (Lot 67, Csd-2249); on the NW., N., along lines 4-5-6, by lot 4412, Pls-45; on the N., along line 7-8 by lot 6162, Pls-45 (Lot 62, Csd-2449); on the E., along line 8-9 Lot 6162 Pls-45; and on the S., along line 9-1 by Lot 6180-B, Csd-04-019187-D. Beginning from point marked “1” on plan being S. 51° 55′ W., 281.58 meters from BLLM No. 112, Pls-45, Calauag Public Land Subdivision, thence:

