LOT NO. 6180-B, CSD-04-019187-D BARANGAY BANTULINAO ELEMENTARY SCHOOL

A PARCEL OF LAND ( Lot No. 6180-B, Csd-04-019187-D, being a portion of Lot 6180, Pls-45, Calauag Public Land Subdivision), situated in Barangay Bantulinao, Municipality of Calauag, Province of Quezon, Island of Luzon. Bounded on the NE., along line 1-2 by Lot 6180-A, Csd-04-019187-D (Bantulinao High School), along line 2-3 by Lot 6162, Pls-45, Calauag Public Land Subdivision (Lot 62, Csd-2449); on the SW., along lines 3-4-5 by Lot 6167 Pls-45 (Lot 67, Csd-2249); and on the N., lines 5-6-1 by Lot 6180-A, Csd-04-019187-D. Beginning from point marked “1” on plan being S. 51° 55′ W., 281.58 meters from BLLM No. 112, Pls-45, Calauag Public Land Subdivision, thence:

