65.07 m. to point of

beginning, containing an area of TEN THOUSAND SIX HUNDRED TWENTY ONE (10,621) SQUARE METERS , more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground as follows; Points 1, 2, 5 , and 6 by PS Cyl. Con. Mons 15 x 40 cm. And the rest are old “BL” Cyl. Conc. Mon. 15 x 60 cm. Bearings: True; Date of Original Survey July 1935 – April 1977 and that of the subdivision survey: December 7, 1998 and was approved on February 9, 1999.

IN WITNESS THEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

The parcels of land herein reserved shall be non-alienable and shall not be subject to occupation, entry, sale, lease or other mode of disposition until again declared as alienable by proclamation of the President.

Done in the City of Manila, this 16th day of June in the year of our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

